implicits

Related Doc: package cats

object implicits extends AllInstances with AllSyntax with cats.instances.AllInstances

Provided for convenience, for importing everything from Cats (all instances, syntax, etc), as well as all defined instances from Monix.

import monix.cats.implicits._
